 This sequence, call it 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

the associated reduced sequence
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{n}=x_{n}-\left\lfloor x_{n}\right\rfloor $
\end_inset

